flowchart LR
    A[Admin Browser] --> S[Doctor Servlet]
    S --> V[DoctorService]
    V --> DD[DoctorDao]
    V --> UD[UserDao]
    V --> DP[DepartmentDao]
    V --> RD[RoleDao]
    DD --> O[(Oracle XE)]
    UD --> O
    DP --> O
    RD --> O

    C[Create] --> CT[USERS + DOCTORS transaction]
    U[Update] --> UT[USERS identity/password + DOCTORS transaction]
    AC[Activate] --> AT[DOCTORS ACTIVE + USERS ACTIVE]
    DE[Deactivate] --> BC{Future appointments or active schedules?}
    BC -->|Yes| BL[Blocked + audit]
    BC -->|No| DT[DOCTORS INACTIVE + USERS INACTIVE]
    CT --> V
    UT --> V
    AT --> V
    BL --> V
    DT --> V
